query:
SELECT g.id, g.userId, u.name, u.email, u.role,
       (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM relatorios_livres WHERE gestorId = g.id) as rel_livres,
       (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM relatorios_completos WHERE gestorId = g.id) as rel_completos
FROM gestores g
LEFT JOIN users u ON g.userId = u.id
